<%- include('partials/header') %>
<style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background: #f8fafc;
        color: #1e293b;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background: #1e293b;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
    }

    nav h2 {
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    nav ul li a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.3s ease, border-bottom 0.3s ease;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
        color: #38bdf8;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #38bdf8;
    }

    /* Content */
    .content {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
    }

    .content h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: #1518d3;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .content h2 {
        margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        color: #1e293b;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        border-left: 5px solid #38bdf8;
        padding-left: 12px;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        border-radius: 6px;
    }

    /* Lists */
    .content ul {
        margin: 1rem 0 2rem 2rem;
        color: #475569;
        list-style: disc;
    }

    .content ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .content ul li:hover {
        transform: translateX(6px);
        color: #1518d3;
    }

    /* Case Study Box */
    .case-study {
        background: #fff;
        border-left: 6px solid #1518d3;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .case-study:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .case-study h3 {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        color: #2563eb;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .case-study p {
        color: #475569;
    }
</style>

<!-- Navbar -->
<nav>
    <h2>Data Privacy Hub</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/solution">Solutions</a></li>
        <li><a href="/issues">Issues</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy-law">Privacy Laws</a></li>
    </ul>
</nav>

<!-- Content -->
<section class="content">
    <h1>Data Privacy Challenges in Education</h1>
    
    <h2>Common Issues in Educational Settings</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Lack of transparency in educational data collection</li>
        <li>Cloud storage risks with student information</li>
        <li>Inconsistent data protection across educational platforms</li>
        <li>Increasing frequency of educational data breaches</li>
        <li>Excessive retention of student records beyond necessary periods</li>
        <li>Privacy challenges from educational technology (EdTech)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Educational Data Breaches</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Unauthorized access to student information systems</li>
        <li>Potential for serious harm including academic identity theft</li>
        <li>Requirement to report breaches involving student data</li>
        <li>Special sensitivity of minors' information in breaches</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Student-Specific Privacy Concerns</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Educational apps collecting excessive personal data</li>
        <li>Learning management systems tracking student behavior</li>
        <li>Sharing student data with third-party educational services</li>
        <li>Online proctoring software privacy issues</li>
        <li>Long-term storage of digital learning analytics</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="case-study">
        <h3>Recruitment Agency Case Study</h3>
        <p>A recruitment agency failed to remove all personal information from an old online profile, highlighting the importance of complete data deletion, especially for students entering the job market.</p>
    </div>
</section>

